+# Rigging
+
+Project tooling values for Shipshape roles. Values only, not procedure.
+Procedure lives in the skills. Every role reads this on open.
+
+## Stack
+
+- language: javascript
+- runtime: node
+- packageManager: npm
+
+## Directories
+
+- implementation: src
+- specs: features
+- verification: features/steps, features/support
+- assets: data
+- scantlings: none
+
+## Commands
+
+- discover: `npx @cucumber/cucumber --dry-run --tags "not @captain and not @shipwright"`
+- focused: `npx @cucumber/cucumber features/{scenario} --tags "not @captain and not @shipwright"`
+- broad: `npx @cucumber/cucumber --tags "not @captain and not @shipwright"`
+- coverage: `npx @cucumber/cucumber --tags "not @captain and not @shipwright"`
+- step-usage: `npx @cucumber/cucumber --format usage-json --tags "not @captain and not @shipwright"`
+- plank-inventory: `grep -rn '@planks' src/`
+- typecheck: none
+- lint: none
+
+## Perturbation
+
+- message: `PERTURBATION: consider current durable context; remove when fixed`
+- perturb: `throw new Error("PERTURBATION: consider current durable context; remove when fixed");`
+
+## Tiers
+
+- default: @logic
+- sandbox: none
+- policy: @logic none
+- weather: none
+- runrecord: none
+
+## Dependencies
+
+- policy: latest-stable
+- dependency: @cucumber/cucumber
+
+## Outbound
+
+- outbound: none
+- ship: none
+- verify: none
